title: Ashley Tisdale rocks chic sleeveless dress after workout
title_page: Ashley Tisdale rocks chic sleeveless dress after workout | Daily Mail Online
text:
She a multi-talented Hollywood star.
So it's little surprise that Ashley Tisdale is prioritizing staying both hip and fit.
The 31-year-old High School Musical star started her Wednesday with a healthy workout in Studio City, California.
Keeping fit! Ashley Tisdale, 31, started her Wednesday with a healthy workout in Studio City, California
The former Disney starlet donned a dark Rangers hoodie for her athletic endeavor, which she paired with some slate grey, cropped leggings and black leather sandals.
Her main accessory was a pair of distinctive, vintage-style shades, though she also toted a very furry key chain.
She also must have worried about hydration, as she carried both a massive bottle of water and a smaller secondary drink container.
Probably for practical reasons, she pulled her brunette tresses back into a messy bun.
Made for walking: A sleeveless black number fell past her knees, which she paired with very ornate black studded booties
Some light blush and nude lipstick made her youthful, post-workout visage glow.
Later, the wife of musician Christopher French swapped out her utilitarian look for a more sophisticated ensemble.
A sleeveless black number fell past her knees, which she paired with very ornate black studded booties.
Locking up her look! She also carried a substantial Louis Vuitton handbag which even sported a small padlock on the front, and shielded her eyes with some fancy gradient sunglasses with gold frames
She also carried a substantial Louis Vuitton handbag which even sported a small padlock on the front, and shielded her eyes with some fancy gradient sunglasses with gold frames.
This time, her caramel locks were parted in the middle and styled into gentle waves.
Meanwhile, the actress has been busy lately lending her voice to the upcoming animated film, Charming.
The actress plays Cinderella in the upcoming animated musical, which boasts a star-studded cast of Demi Lovato, Wilmer Valderrama, and Sia.
